data.description: Already booked for the US Open! Don't let this incredible opportunity slip through your fingers to own a fully furnished, turnkey investment property primed to bolster your portfolio. Ever dreamed of owning a certified Pinehurst Short-Term Rental (STR)? Now's your chance to seize a stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom short-term rental in the Historic Village of Pinehurst. Perfect for investors eyeing a seamless blend of investment potential and golf vacation allure, this spacious retreat embodies comfort, convenience, and quintessential Southern charm. Everything you see is included! We kindly ask that you respect our guests' privacy by refraining from unannounced visits to the property. For further details or investment numbers, please have your agent reach out to us.
